```mermaid
flowchart TD
    %% Input
    Input[("User/Tool Events")]
    
    %% Extraction
    Input --> Extractor["MemoryExtractor\n(LLM-based)"]
    Extractor -->|analyzes| ToolCalls["Tool Calls\n+ Results"]
    Extractor -->|analyzes| Errors["Errors\n+ Fixes"]
    Extractor -->|analyzes| Patterns["Patterns\n+ Decisions"]
    
    %% Output: Structured Memories
    Extractor --> Episodic["Episodic\n(what happened"]
    Extractor --> Procedural["how we did it"]
    Extractor --> Semantic["facts/conventions"]
    Extractor --> Lessons["lessons learned"]
    
    %% Storage
    Episodic --> PG[("PostgreSQL\nmemories table")]
    Procedural --> PG
    Semantic --> PG
    Lessons --> PG
    
    %% Retrieval
    PG --> Recall["ContextRecall\n(recallMemories)"]
    Recall -->|semantic search| Results["Relevant Memories"]
    
    %% Injection
    Results --> Priming["PrimingEngine\n(buildPrimingContext)"]
    Priming --> Injected[("Injected into\nAgent Context")]
    
    %% Background Processing
    PG -.-> Subconscious["Subconscious\n(periodic)"]
    Subconscious -->|distills| Distilled["Distilled Summaries"]
    Subconscious -->|extracts| Lessons
    Distilled --> PG
    
    %% TTL Cleanup
    PG -.->|TTL expiry| Cleanup["cleanup()\ndeletes old"]
    
    classDef proc fill:#0f172a,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef mem fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#22d3ee,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef store fill:#450a0a,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    classDef bg fill:#064e3b,stroke:#10b981,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    
    class Extractor,Recall,Priming proc
    class Episodic,Procedural,Semantic,Lessons,Results,Distilled mem
    class PG store
    class Subconscious,Cleanup bg
```